 class="mceBlockContainer" valign="top"><div data-block-id="3" class="mceText" id="dataBlockId-3" style="width:100%"><p style="text-align: left;">Hello {{ $username }}, </p><p style="text-align: left;"><br/></p><p style="text-align: left;">We noticed that your experience <strong>{{$experienceName}}</strong> on Meet People isn’t fully completed yet — but no worries, we're here to help you make it absolutely amazing! 💫</p><p style="text-align: left;"><br/></p><p style="text-align: left;">Because we want your experience to be as unique as you are, here are a few simple tips to help you out: </p>  @foreach($reason as $r) <ul><li><p style="text-align: left;"> {{$r}}</p></li></ul>   @endforeach   <p style="text-align: left;"><br/></p><p style="text-align: left;">And most importantly, make sure you’ve filled in all the matching criteria to attract the travelers who are the perfect fit for you.</p><p style="text-align: left;"><br/></p><p style="text-align: left;">Need help or looking for inspiration? Our team is here to support you — just drop us a message at <a href="mailto:contact@meetpe.fr">contact@meetpe.fr</a> 🧡</p><p style="text-align: left;"><br/></p><p style="text-align: left;">We can’t wait to see what magical experience you’re going to share. </p><p style="text-align: left;"><br/></p><p style="text-align: left;">Good vibes, </p><p style="text-align: left;" class="last-child">{!! __('general.meet_people_team') !!} 🚀</p></div></td></tr><tr><td style="padding-top:12px;padding-bottom:12px;padding-right:0;padding-left:0" class="mceLayoutContainer" valign="top"><table align="center" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%" role="presentation" data-block-id="19" id="section_d496b9a8a67d3924fb27c55ad81b3aec" class="mceLayout"><tbody><tr class="mceRow"><td style="background-position:center;background-repeat:no-repeat;background-size:cover" valign="top"><table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%" role="presentation"><tbody><tr><td class="mc